				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: for all you high lvls<a name="37445"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 30 04 4:28 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I didn't mention the Wristsnapper as they still go for a good amt of plat in bazaar (on veeshan anyway)
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">ALSO.. how much would that stuff be..? i only have 301 PP on exes(36 wiz) and i need some for spells.. thanx</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
300p should be enough to get you a Shaded Dagger, Shaded Blade or a Centi Shortsword.
<br />

<br />
A good way to earn cash at low levels is to farm tradeskill drops like spider/spiderling/shade/shadeling silks...
<br />
If you don't like farming and selling crap in bazaar, you can whack mobs in Qeynos noobie yard... the snakes often drop 5gp vendor trash and rats can drop 1p junk. Save the snake eggs too... there's a decent market for them on some servers. Whenever I start a noob on a new server, I always level up in the Qeynos noob yard... 50pp by level 5 is an attainable goal.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
