				<td colspan="2"><span>Once you are 15, and have your mez song, that combined with your lvl 8 Lull song will make you the Puller and Crowd Controller for groups.  Especially once you can do LDoN.  Pulling and CC for groups is what has kept my Defense skill maxed.  You get beat on enough on pulls, and when locking down adds, but you also have a healer with you.
<br />

<br />
If your weapon skills are still crappy by the time you ding 26, Snare/Fear kiting is an excellent way to bring them up.  Get a shammy DEX buff before you head out, if you can.  Then go somewhere like LOIO or the Gnoll Spires in SK, and twist Snare, Fear, and Chant of Battle (for DEX, but only if you are not getting resists on your other songs!)  I did a lot of instrument twisting in groups early on, so my weapon skills were poor by lvl 26.  This method brought them up nicely.
<br />

<br />
As for the instrument skills, check the guides.  I wrote a guide about AFK Training that has everything you need to know about keeping your Instrument Skills maxed out.</span></td>
